code: import{RoomObjectCategory}from'@nitrots/nitro-renderer';import{GetRoomSession,GetSessionDataManager}from'../session';import{GetRoomEngine}from'./GetRoomEngine';export function GetOwnRoomObject(){var userId=GetSessionDataManager().userId;var roomId=GetRoomEngine().activeRoomId;var category=RoomObjectCategory.UNIT;var totalObjects=GetRoomEngine().getTotalObjectsForManager(roomId,category);var i=0;while(i<totalObjects){var roomObject=GetRoomEngine().getRoomObjectByIndex(roomId,i,category);if(roomObject){var userData=GetRoomSession().userDataManager.getUserDataByIndex(roomObject.id);if(userData){if(userData.webID===userId)return roomObject;}}i++;}return null;}
